NK015(ba)017:3: las sngags kyi bsnyen pa dang gsum /
NK015(ba)017:5: phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin gyis yid sgrib sbyangs pa ni /
NK015(ba)017:6: sems dpa' gsum brtsegs kyi h'u mthar /
NK015(ba)017:7: ru lu 'bru brgyad g.yas bskor du 'khor ba /
NK015(ba)017:10: las 'phros h'u la thim par bsam pa sogs 'bru re re nas bsgom /
NK015(ba)017:11: dus cig char h'u las 'od zer brgyad sros 'bru brgyad la thim /
NK015(ba)017:12: 'bru brgyad las re re 'phros h'u la thim par bsam ste /
NK015(ba)017:14: ngag bzlas bya tshul bzhi las /
NK015(ba)017:15: dang po thabs dang shes rab steng sgo dbye ba'i bzlas pa ni /
NK015(ba)017:16: yab yum gyi mgrin par pad+ma 'dab brgyad steng /
NK015(ba)017:17: ljags rdo rje rtse gsum par bsam pa h'u la /
NK015(ba)017:19: yab kyi thugs kar rdo rje'i dbus de ltar bsam pa'i /
NK015(ba)017:20: dbus kyi h'u las 'od mthing 'phros 'bru brgyad la g.yas bskor gyis /
NK015(ba)017:22: ye shes sems dpa' gtsug gtor nas thon /
NK015(ba)017:23: ljags kyi 'bru brgyad la g.yas su bskor zhal nas thon /
NK015(ba)017:24: yum gyi zhal gyi ljags kyi rdo rje'i rtse nas /
NK015(ba)017:25: lte bar 'bru brgyad la g.yon du bskor /
NK015(ba)017:27: thugs ka'i b+han+d+ha'i nang gi h'u la 'bru brgyad kyis bskor bar /
NK015(ba)017:28: thugs rgyud bskul ba'i tshul gyis g.yon du bskor nas /
NK015(ba)017:29: tshur yab kyi thugs kar byung ste yang sngar bzhin bskor ro //
NK015(ba)017:30: de la sngags tshar bzhi re ste /
NK015(ba)017:31: de nyid 'bum mam bye ba bsnyen /
NK015(ba)017:32: gnyis pa byang chub sems kyis mchod pa 'bul ba'i bzlas pa ni /
NK015(ba)017:33: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rjer h'u la 'bru brgyad kyi bskor bar bsam /
NK015(ba)017:34: yab kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer mar brgyud /
NK015(ba)017:35: gsang ba'i 'bru brgyad la g.yas su 'khor /
NK015(ba)017:36: rdo rje'i dbus rwa nas zhugs /
NK015(ba)017:40: ljags kyi 'bru brgyad la g.yon du 'khor /
NK015(ba)017:41: yab kyi ljags la g.yas su 'khor /
NK015(ba)017:42: mar rgyud thugs kar 'khor te bar ma chad par bsam ste /
NK015(ba)017:44: gsum pa dngos grub yum gyi mkha' nas blang ba'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK015(ba)017:45: yab kyi thugs ka nas yar brgyud /
NK015(ba)017:47: yum gyi ljags la g.yon bskor /
NK015(ba)017:51: dbus rwar bzhugs g.yas bskor gyis /
NK015(ba)017:52: yar rgyud thugs kar bskor ba bar ma chad par /
NK015(ba)017:54: bzhi pa bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i 'phro 'dus ye shes kyi lha mnyes pa sgrub pa ni /
NK015(ba)017:55: ye shes pa mdun mkhar bzhugs pa'i zhal nas phar tshur du brgyud de /
NK015(ba)017:56: bdag gi thugs kar g.yas su 'khor /
NK015(ba)017:57: mdun gyi thugs kar g.yon du bskor te /
NK015(ba)017:60: rang sngags kyi bsnyen pa bya ba ni /
NK015(ba)017:61: yab rnams la ru lu'i mthar rang sngags g.yas bskor /
NK015(ba)017:62: yum rnams la ru lu'i mthar rang sngags g.yon bskor bsam /
NK015(ba)017:64: zhal nas yum gyi thugs kar g.yon bskor gyis tshur thugs kar g.yas bskor bya /
NK015(ba)017:66: yab kyi thugs kar g.yas bskor gyis ljags nas brgyud /
NK015(ba)017:67: yum gyi thugs kar g.yon bskor du bsam /
NK015(ba)017:68: ma mo rnams rang rang thugs kar bskor ba'i 'od zer gtso bo'i thugs kar bstim par bsam ste /
NK015(ba)017:69: 'bum dang bye ba gtso 'khor 'gros ltar bazla'o //
NK015(ba)017:70: stong mtshams su mchod bstod re bya dgos so //
